{"tid":1002683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬些路太太掛住C朗：好失落","createTime":"2019-01-31T06:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T10:38:31.000Z","uid":54373,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"991e52a0b630ae0acf9132391e326b8eb9049855","tid":1002683,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cni6Zp7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCni6Zp7.jpg&h=38cae8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.taghobby.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taghobby.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F029.jpg&h=4675efb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6uu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=3d0be2a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里後衛馬些路的太太Alves坦言，自從基斯坦奴朗拿度離隊，整個生活變得很失落。<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里球星馬些路（Marcelo）的太太Clarice Alves，日前接受訪問時透露基斯坦奴朗拿度離隊後，生活變得失落得多。原來，馬些路一家和C朗全家很好感情，「我跟他媽媽很熟稔，Georgina（C朗女友）也很好人，我兒子跟他小兒子很夾得來，所以全家感到有點無所適從，覺得很失落。」 Alves是巴西藝人，2006年陪伴馬些路移居馬德里，當年她才18歲，兩人目前養育兩個兒子，她的最新電影作品將在今年推出。原來她不是足球迷，但每場皇馬主場比賽，她都帶兒子亮相打氣。 她又透露皇馬的WAGs們都很團結。「我跟不少球員女伴都是好朋友，好像莫迪歷的太太Vanjia、基羅拿華斯的太太Andrea。我在這兒已經12年了，跟每一個人都很熟稔。」"},{"pid":"bc8a45d0c72754c672c6923b28d7de47f43cea54","tid":1002683,"uid":31208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414a7f189cfae6b42fa4a8b85f42b035f828b84d","tid":1002683,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faefd7b780467d1ddb3f0bd86ee9044eb4f25eb","tid":1002683,"uid":53238